\f0\b\fs24 \cf0 WormAngles\

\b0 script RunAllSkeletons runs through all the codes to calculate angle time series of worm images \
(which are stored in the Parallel WormTracker format with additional modification to save binary images)\
save data per experiment as WormGeomTracks.\
Steps:\
- FindAllWormSkeletonsFromTracks\
  calculates the skeletons from binary worm images from tracks_als files.\
- correctAngles\
  smoothes skeleton, divides skeleton into segments of equal arc length and calculates angles in rad.\
- HeadAssign;\
  finds head coordinates of worm.\
- skel_order;\
  orders skeleton from head to tail and fixes left-right flips. \

