EigenwormDecomposition\

\b0 includes the following main scripts:\
\
- GetEigenworm_fromCombinedTracks\
  calculates eigenworms from input angle time series (from format: WormGeomTracks)\
\
- EigenWormProjectiosScript_ontoFixedEWs\
  projects angle time series onto input eigenworms and outputs time series of undulation mode and turning mode per track,\
  saves them as EigenWormTracks; \
  calculates matrices of body, undulation and turning amplitudes;\
  saves data from all experiments.\
\
- EigenWormProjectiosScript_fixedEWs_forGradients_PerFile\
  projects angle time series onto input eigenworms and outputs time series of undulation mode and turning mode per track,\
  also saves body posture (= raw angle data)\
  saves data per experiment as EigenWormTracks.\
  Input for GradientAnalysis/ TurningMode/ BodyTurningxBearing\
\
- EigenWormProjectiosScript_fxedEWs_PhaseSpeed\
  calculates phase speed (= undulation frequency) by projecting angle time series onto input eigenworms.\
\
Further this folder includes the decomposition sub-functions performing the eigenworm calculations;\
and other used sub-functions.\

